<para style="q1">

<verse number="21" style="v" />They open their mouths wide against me;</para>

<para style="q1">they said, "Aha, Aha, our eyes have seen it."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="22" style="v" />You have seen it, Yahweh, do not be silent;</para>

<para style="q1">Lord, do not be far from me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="23" style="v" />Arouse yourself and awake to my defense;</para>

<para style="q1">My God and my Lord, defend my cause.</para>
